Package: pmcexplore
Title: Handle Text Data from PubMed Central
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Natalie",
           family = "Gable",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "natalie.gable@nih.gov")
Description: Handle Text Data from PubMed Central. This package provides functions to search PMC, load full-text XMLs from PMC, and handle text data within R. All data loading uses the Entrez Programming Utilities (E-utilities) API from the NCBI to query and fetch text data from the PMC database. It can fetch sections of a full-text document, such as metadata, data availability statement, and abstract. It also implements text embeddings and preprocessing steps so that text data can be used in models. 
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
